      },
      {
        q: 'How do I see which classrooms are practicing?',
        a: 'Your school dashboard shows daily practice minutes, sessions completed, and the percent of classrooms active in the past 7 and 30 days. Drill into any classroom for detail.',
      },
      {
        q: 'Can I assign a theme building-wide?',
        aHtml:
          'Yes. Pick a weekly or monthly theme — like <em>Kindness</em>, <em>Focus</em>, or <em>Gratitude</em> — and every classroom in your school will see that theme surfaced when they open Inner Explorer.',
      },
      {
        q: 'Can counselors and behavior staff use it?',
        a: 'Yes — counselors get specialized access to short, regulation-focused practices appropriate for small-group and one-on-one sessions, in addition to the full classroom library.',
      },
      {
        q: 'Can I onboard new teachers mid-year?',
        a: 'Yes. New staff can be added at any time at no additional cost. We send them a self-serve orientation and check in after their first two weeks of practice.',
