      {
        q: 'What does success look like in year one?',
        a: 'Most schools target 80% of classrooms practicing at least three days per week by month three. We help you set realistic milestones and track them in your dashboard.',
      },
      {
        q: 'How do I encourage consistency across classrooms?',
        a: 'The most consistent buildings share two habits: a school-wide anchor time (often right after morning announcements) and brief weekly check-ins at staff meetings. Our partner success team will share playbooks from comparable schools.',
      },
      {
        q: 'Can I download a report for my school board?',
        a: 'Yes. Generate a one-page PDF impact report — with practice minutes, classroom adoption, and benchmark research outcomes — directly from your dashboard.',
      },
