  {
    id: 'district-dashboard',
    label: 'District dashboard',
    title: 'District dashboard',
    items: [
      {
        q: 'What does the district dashboard show?',
        a: 'Adoption funnels across every school, total Mindful Minutes practiced, classroom and educator counts, theme trends, and an impact view that ties practice consistency to research-backed outcomes.',
      },
      {
        q: 'Can I compare schools?',
        a: 'Yes — the school grid view ranks adoption and engagement across every site, with filters by level (elementary, middle, high) and Title I status.',
