      {
        q: 'How often does data refresh?',
        a: 'Engagement data refreshes nightly. Practice sessions appear in the dashboard within a few minutes of being completed.',
      },
      {
        q: 'Can I export the data?',
        a: 'Yes. Every report exports to CSV or a board-ready PDF. We can also push aggregated, de-identified metrics to your district’s data warehouse on request.',
