        q: 'Does the dashboard support multi-year reporting?',
        a: 'Yes. Year-over-year views are available once your district has at least one full academic year of practice data.',
      },
      {
        q: 'What about ESSER or grant reporting?',
        a: 'We provide pre-built ESSER and Title IV reporting templates with all the engagement and outcome data your grants office needs. Many districts use Inner Explorer to satisfy mental-health and SEL grant requirements.',
