        q: 'What outcomes have studies shown?',
        a: 'Documented outcomes include improvements in attention and academic performance, reductions in behavioral referrals, lower teacher stress, and improvements in school climate. Effect sizes vary by population and dosage; we publish all study summaries openly.',
      },
      {
        q: 'Is Inner Explorer ESSA-aligned?',
        a: 'Inner Explorer meets ESSA Tier 2 (Moderate Evidence) and Tier 3 (Promising Evidence) criteria depending on the outcome measured. Citations and the underlying studies are available on request.',
