      {
        q: 'How is "Mindful Minutes" calculated?',
        a: 'Each completed practice contributes its play duration multiplied by an estimated class size. Districts can supply exact class sizes for more precise reporting; otherwise we use grade-band averages.',
      },
      {
        q: 'Can I run a custom study in my district?',
        aHtml:
          'Yes. Our research team partners with several districts each year on custom IRB-approved evaluations. Reach out through the <em>Partnering with us</em> section below.',
      },
    ],
  },
