      },
      {
        q: 'What student data does Inner Explorer collect?',
        a: 'In the standard configuration, none. Students do not log in or create accounts. We only collect classroom-level practice metadata (which practices played, when, for how long) tied to an educator account.',
      },
      {
        q: 'Do you sell or share data?',
        aHtml:
          'Never. We do not sell, rent, or share student or educator data with third parties for advertising or marketing. Full details are in our <a href="/privacy">privacy policy</a>.',
      },
      {
        q: 'Where is data stored?',
        a: 'On encrypted servers in the United States, hosted with SOC 2 Type II–certified cloud providers. All data is encrypted in transit (TLS 1.2+) and at rest (AES-256).',
